        <title>Portal and Half life movie!</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Banethulhu]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Star Trek, Star Wars, Half-Life, wow this guy is gaining so much power in so little time.</p>
<p>I’d actually be more interested in seeing them make a game together (which they also discussed) than a movie.</p>
<p>If they did make a movie I’d like to see it set in the half-life timeline and not be like an adaptation of half-life 1 (for example), I’d love to see it set between half-life 1 and 2 when the combine started invading and have the main character someone new or even maybe barney.</p>
