        <title>Portal and Half life movie!</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[M-Man]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I think it could be really cool if done right.  I’d like a story of some security gurads and scientists during the Black Mesa incident.  Of course we’d only barely glimpse Gordon (maybe in a security camera, or briefly in person).  He would be more of a plot device than a character.</p>
<p>We’d follow this guard as he tries to escape, but then he decides he needs to do something to save the other people there. Eventually he’d get rescued by Gordon, (you’d have to find a good moment of a guard in the game. Maybe the one who is running from soldiers in ST?).</p>
